description.en: Coupit is a decentralized incentive platform that utilizes the NEO blockchain,  thereby reducing third party interaction while providing a transparent  operational system. Coupit marketplace UI (User-Interface) and UE (User- Experience) are designed in a way that gives significant accessibility and  incentives to both the businesses and users registered under the Coupit platform.
